project_descr: The project aims to to enhance the capacity of human rights and justice institutions and UNDP Country Offices to pursue a robust regime of  human rights, rule of law and justice programming in support of country level engagements.

outputs.output_descr: Selected institutions and organizations of the NHR Protection Systems in ECIS are better able to use their mandate and available resources for the development of long-term strategies to promote and protect human rights at the national level.
Increased capacity of UNDP’s Country Offices to support national engagements with International Human Rights and Justice Principles and Mechanisms.
donor_name: GLOBAL FUND TO FIGHT AIDS, TUBERCULOSIS

outputs.output_descr: Increased capacity of UNDP’s Country Offices in supporting national partners for improving rule of law and justice services.

project_title: strengthening national human rights & justice systems
